12#ifndef MODULES_RTP_RTCP_SOURCE_RTCP_PACKET_COMPOUND_PACKET_H_
13#define MODULES_RTP_RTCP_SOURCE_RTCP_PACKET_COMPOUND_PACKET_H_
14
15#include <memory>
16#include <vector>
17
18#include "modules/rtp_rtcp/source/rtcp_packet.h"
19#include "rtc_base/constructor_magic.h"
20
21namespace webrtc {
22namespace rtcp {
23
24class CompoundPacket : public RtcpPacket {
25 public:
26 CompoundPacket();
27 ~CompoundPacket() override;
28
29 void Append(std::unique_ptr<RtcpPacket> packet);
30
31 // Size of this packet in bytes (i.e. total size of nested packets).
32 size_t BlockLength() const override;
33 // Returns true if all calls to Create succeeded.
34 bool Create(uint8_t* packet,
35 size_t* index,
36 size_t max_length,
37 PacketReadyCallback callback) const override;
38
39 protected:
40 std::vector<std::unique_ptr<RtcpPacket>> appended_packets_;
41
42 private:
43 RTC_DISALLOW_COPY_AND_ASSIGN(CompoundPacket);
44};
45
46} // namespace rtcp
47} // namespace webrtc
48#endif // MODULES_RTP_RTCP_SOURCE_RTCP_PACKET_COMPOUND_PACKET_H_
